OL,5, Conservative MP Michael Frabricant has 
OL,6, apologised for suggesting teachers and 
OL,7, nurses enjoyed a "quiet drink" in      
OL,8, staff-rooms during lockdown.           
OL,10,FHe had made the comments in a BBC      
OL,11,Finterview while defending Boris Johnson
OL,12,Fover so-called Partygate allegations.  
OL,14,FIn a letter to the NAHT school leaders'
OL,15,Funion, the Lichfield MP said it was not
OL,16,Fhis intention to demoralise or offend  
OL,17,Fanyone.                                
OL,19,FNAHT general secretary Paul Whiteman   
OL,20,Fsaid he welcomed the apology.          
